 {"id":"bd-yx9r.6","title":"Runtime, trace, lab, and util completion beyond current kernel scaffolding","description":"The current C tree has scheduler/cancel/timer/quiescence and some runtime-side helpers, but the upstream crate still exposes much broader runtime/reactor/trace/lab/util surfaces: runtime builders, local runtimes, spawn_blocking, task handles/tables, deadline monitors, advanced trace analysis, replayers/minimizers, lab network/http/meta tooling, and deterministic utilities.","design":"This epic should close the gap between a functioning kernel and the broader runtime/tooling system users expect from the crate.","acceptance_criteria":"A. Missing runtime/trace/lab/util public families are represented concretely in ANSI C.\\nB. Determinism, replay, and diagnostic claims are backed by richer trace/lab evidence than the current kernel-only lanes.\\nC. Higher-surface networking/protocol work can build on these runtime/tooling primitives.","notes":"Primary upstream references: src/runtime/*, src/runtime/reactor/*, src/trace/*, src/lab/*, src/util/*.","status":"open","priority":0,"issue_type":"epic","created_at":"2026-03-13T20:38:23.700831656Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-03-13T20:41:06.166054052Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["crate-parity","lab","runtime","trace"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.6","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-03-13T20:38:23.700831656Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.6","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-13T20:39:02.497407280Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.6","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.2","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-13T20:39:03.461678881Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-yx9r.6","depends_on_id":"bd-yx9r.3","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-13T20:39:04.462855809Z","created_by":"ub